{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"continueTransaction"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Bool","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The messages within a transaction carry the cumulative values of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a field. In case one or more messages within a transaction are not","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"received by the Server (e.g., as a result of radio collisions),","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the next received message will make up for the lost messages,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"carrying cumulative values of the field."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A new transaction is started when this field is set to ","type":"text"},{"code":"true","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":",","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"or when the last message of the transaction was sent 6 or","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"more seconds earlier.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This defaults to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"false"},{"type":"text","text":", which means that each new message will"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"receive a new transaction identifier (if not set explicitly)."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/GenericDeltaSetUnacknowledged\/continueTransaction","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/genericdeltasetunacknowledged\/continuetransaction"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths